metadata.name: Commit to Happiness
metadata.description:
Commit to what you love-- be it a cause, a project, another person, or even yourself. Your memories will guide you if you don't let them hold you back!

A change is coming, a change started by your own choice. You may not see it now, but if you stay true to your decision you will walk the path to wealth, prosperity and happiness.

Card: The Fairy Bride - Victorian Fairy deck
Fortune read 03/29/2022

Symbols: bride, forget-me-nots, butterfly, key, goldenrod, pearls
